Yep----

And I found this all out just like a dummy-----

I flat towed a Buick Special to Florida, from Chicago, back in the late
70's without taking the driveshaft out.

Got there just fine----But when I went to drive the car--- all the 2
speed trans could do was---WIRRRRRRRRRRR.

Hmm, I says to myself--"musta cooked the trans." :>( 

Another fine learning experience, in my youth-----

