Flat towing an automatic anything without the axles, driveshaft removed,
will guarantee, a fried pump in the trans. 

and EVERY auto tranny that I have had go out has been a failed tranny
pump. =A0 and it is VERY VERY diffcult to repair/replace as it is all
the way at the back (front) of the tranny, every other part has to be
removed. 
